profile:
Five Star Painting is a locally owned and operated house painting company servicing the West GTA Area.
 
As a part of an international painting franchise system, we give you the peace of mind knowing that we're not a "fly-by-night" contractor that will cut corners or leave the job incomplete. 
 
We provide: 
FREE COLOUR CONSULTATION session with our INTERIOR DESIGNER
PREMIUM ENVIRONMENT-FRIENDLY ZERO VOC PAINTS
 
EXTENDED MANUFACTURER PAINT WARRANTY
EXTENDED LABOUR WARRANTY 
 
QUALIFIED PAINTERS
 
ON-TIME GUARANTEE
BEST PRICE GUARANTEE
 
Thorough Surface Preparation 
A responsive management team should there be any challenges 
Detailed pricing that lets you know what you are getting for your money
 
We are available 24/7 to take your call. Our customer service department will ask for some basic information about your project and will schedule one of our estimators to come out to discuss your project. Our estimators will confirm your appointment, show up on time, and will provide you a detailed quote of the work discussed. It's that simple! 

We are a licensed and insured company that distinguishes our company from smaller and insecure businesses.

We strive to exceed your expectations and focus all of our energy and resources on delivering outstanding results.

profile:
ALF PAINTING SERVICE

If you're looking for a professional painting and home renovation company with years of experience to prove it, then look no further, ALF Painters is the contractor for you. We specialize in interior, exterior, residential, and commercial painting and our services don't stop there! We can also help you with drywall repair and installation, plaster, stucco ceiling repair and removal, carpentry, Kitchen Cabinet repainting, hardwood flooring and much more! Call one of our customer service experts now and be well on your way to a quote and a beautifully transformed property.

Serving Toronto, Mississauga and the grater GTA area!

Remember when you go with ALF Painting Service we value your business and referrals and are committed to getting it done right the first time. GUARANTEED!

Why use Home Painters to paint your house/office?
•Two Year Guarantee On All Work Done
•Full Workers Compensation
•5 Million Liability Insurance
•Fully Bonded Workers (Criminal Background Checks on ALL Workers)
•Thousands of Satisfied Clients
•Top Quality Paints Used Including Benjamin Moore, Dulux, Behr, Sherwin Williams, Para etc
•Drop sheets to Protect Your Floors and Belongings
•100% Satisfaction Guaranteed!!

Interior Painting Services Include:
•Painting (i.e. walls, trim, doors, floors, ceilings, etc.)
•Staining (i.e. banisters, hardwood floors, cabinets, etc.)
•Faux finishing
•Stucco Painting and Repair
•Wallpapering and Removal
•Drywall Repair and Replacement
•Plaster

Exterior Painting Services Include:
•Painting Exterior Surfaces (ie. windows, brick, doors, eaves, soffits, aluminum siding, etc.)
•Deck/Fence Staining and Refinishing
•Power Washing
•Caulking
•Rotten Wood Replacement/Repair

Hey! Arran MacDonald here. Thank you for taking the time to check out our business. 

I began painting in university for a local business while I was finishing my bachelors degree. I quickly gained a passion for providing exceptional results for my clients. There is no better feeling than producing a product that a client loves. That is what I love to do! 

Here at HECRA, we pride ourselves on not only providing exceptional results, but providing our clients with tremendous customer service. 

You matter. We value you and your happiness. We believe that open communication and honesty lead to the BEST service experience. Please do not hestiate to ask questions or express concerns. WE WANT YOU TO BE HAPPY!

We look forward to working with you!

profile:
Welcome TC Contracting 

We offer many Services:

Retaining walls: TC Contracting are specialist in Armour stone, interlock and Pre cast concrete retaining walls.  Whether its aesthetic, or structural  needs, TC Contracting has the skills and knowledge to complete the task. Contact us with your ideas and watch us bring them to reality. 

Full Landscaping , Interlock, Concrete: We know you work hard to see your dream property come to reality. Here at TC, we will work with you to make sure the job is done properly and in a timely matter

Fencing: To dig and set post to complete fencing jobs. From 10 feet to a 1000 feet .  TC has the capabilities to finish your project. Many different fencing designs available, contact us to get started 
Decks: There are many options when it comes to decks IE: Wood type, railings, Steps, Levels ECT. Let TC Contracting's team help you figure out which options are suited best for you!  

Excavation and Trenching: Are you looking for a trusted contractor to excavate your next  project? There are many laws and regulations surrounding excavating and digging. Let us explain what needs to be done and leave it with TC so you are confident  that your job is being done right.  Each and every time!

Gravel Driveways and Sodding: Looking to give your property a beautiful new look? TC Contracting are experts at gravel driveways and sod. We work with our partners to guarantee the best materials at the best prices.

profile:
Sivas Painting Inc team is proud to be one of the most modern lead painting companies in the city.

We at the Sivas Painting Inc company are pleased to offer you a wide professional variety of painting services. We strive to hire only the best painters to take care of all our residential & commercial house projects.

We value both the technical and aesthetic sides of our job in every Showcase… Our board of members, managers, as well as all the painters all firmly stand behind the quality control process, and have the drive to keep perfection and passion at every step. This is evident if you take a short glimpse of our “Project Image Gallery”, that highlights our craftsmanship and professional edge.

ENVIRONMENT FRIENDLINESS
Where our competitors adhere to the regular standards of work, … we strive to match those and beat all expectations by ensuring the best practices for environmental friendly work ethics. What you see as the final work, also has a lot of care and thought process to make sure the jobs are done with the up most respect and care for the environment.

SEASONED PROFESSIONALS
We ensure that our employees are not just amateur painters! We dive deep into a training program for our employees to dive deep into the technicality of paint – among many which include: Color Matching, Functionality / Design Based Paint Selection, Technical aspects of application, Environmental Policies Adherence, …….much much more..We are therefore, very proud and depend a great deal on the professional rarity of our employees – so we also take a bold stand on providing all our projects with a warranty that you can lean on.
name: Sivas Painting Inc.
